## Modulation
Low-frequency signals cannot radiate efficiently, so they ride on a high-frequency **carrier**.

| Type | What varies |
| --- | --- |
| Amplitude (AM) | Carrier amplitude |
| Frequency (FM) | Carrier frequency |
| Phase (PM) | Carrier phase |

