| Enthalpy | Low | High |
| Specificity | Low | High |
| Temperature | Favoured by low T | Needs higher T |

## Adsorption Isotherm
```
Freundlich:  x/m = k * P^(1/n)      (n > 1)
```

The extent of adsorption rises with pressure but levels off as the surface saturates.

