| Abundant | Plentiful |
| Candid | Frank |
| Lethargic | Sluggish |
| Augment | Increase |
| Benevolent | Kind |

## High-Frequency Antonyms
| Word | Antonym |
| --- | --- |
| Transparent | Opaque |
| Optimist | Pessimist |
| Condemn | Praise |
| Frugal | Extravagant |
