  ('ssc-cgl-english-sentence-improvement-spelling-m01', 'ssc-cgl-english-sentence-improvement-spelling', 'Sentence Improvement & Spelling', '**Sentence improvement** asks you to replace an underlined part with the most correct, concise option; **spelling** items test commonly misspelt words.

