  ('ssc-cgl-english-reading-comprehension-m01', 'ssc-cgl-english-reading-comprehension', 'Reading Comprehension', '**Reading comprehension (RC)** measures how well you extract meaning, tone and detail from a passage under time pressure.

## Question Types
| Type | What it asks |
| --- | --- |
| Factual | a detail stated directly |
| Inference | a logical implication |
| Vocabulary | meaning of a word in context |
