  ('gate-general-aptitude-data-interpretation-m01', 'gate-general-aptitude-data-interpretation', 'Data Interpretation', '**Data interpretation** asks you to read tables, charts and graphs and compute quickly — a high-yield GATE aptitude skill.

## Chart Types
