  ('jee-chemistry-amines-q01', 'jee-chemistry-amines', 'Amines are basic because nitrogen has a:', 'Vacant orbital', 'Lone pair of electrons', 'Positive charge', 'Triple bond', 'B', 'The lone pair on nitrogen accepts a proton, making amines basic.', 0),
