  ('jee-chemistry-amines-q07', 'jee-chemistry-amines', 'Diazonium salts are useful chiefly because they undergo:', 'Only combustion', 'No reactions', 'Coupling and substitution reactions', 'Polymerisation only', 'C', 'Diazonium salts couple to form dyes and undergo substitution to add many groups.', 6),
